      "ECT": "agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM \u2192 HYBRID. Placeholder $0.",
      "Home_Health": "agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM \u2192 HYBRID. Placeholder $0.",
      "COVID": "agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=MAX \u2192 MAX. But CASE produces binary 0/1 only \u2192 INDICATOR_FLAG. Placed in indicator_flag_categories only.",
      "AS_slot_composite": "AS is a WINDOW_REDUCTION: LEAD slots AS1-AS10 are individually MAX-aggregated in AGGREGATE_DATE and the composite MAX(AS1)+...+MAX(AS10) is the AGGREGATE_DATE output. The encounter-level step sums this composite across dates (SUM of the date-level composites). This is the standard WINDOW_REDUCTION pattern \u2014 classified as WINDOW_REDUCTION, not HYBRID.",
      "Mammography_Reduction_slot_composite": "Same WINDOW_REDUCTION pattern as AS via Rad1-Rad10 slots.",
      "line_level_source_table_column_check": "#Step3 is built with an EXPLICIT COLUMN LIST from #Step2. It does NOT use SELECT *. The explicit list includes: EncounterID, ServiceDate, OP_Default, AS1-AS10 (LEAD slots), Rad1-Rad10 (LEAD slots), Mammography_NoReduction, Fee_Schedule, ER, AS_Default, Cardiac_Cath, PTCA, EPS, Lithotripsy, Gamma_Knife, Implants, Blood, Drugs, Chemotherapy, Lab, Clinic, Hyperbaric, IV_Therapy, IOP, Partial_Hospitalization, Observation, Psych, ECT, Miscellaneous, Home_Health, COVID. ABSENT from #Step3: RevenueCode, ProcedureCode, Sequence, Amount, BillCharges, Quantity, Modifier1, ServiceDateFrom, ServiceDateTo, OriginalPayment, ProcedureCodeNumeric, ASC_Group, Plan, Payer01Code, Payer01Name, AGE, Mammography_Reduction raw column (replaced by Rad slots), AS raw column (replaced by AS slots). EPS uses BillCharges in LINE_PRICING (Round(BillCharges * 0.74, 2)) \u2014 BillCharges is NOT present in #Step3. A JOIN back to #Step1_Charges or #Step2 is required for BillCharges if EPS LinePayment is to be recomputed at line level. All LEAD slot columns (AS1-AS10, Rad1-Rad10) ARE present in #Step3 confirming it is the correct source.",
      "line_level_has_narrow_column_list": true,
      "narrow_list_payment_columns_requiring_join": [
        "BillCharges (needed for EPS = Round(BillCharges * 0.74, 2)); source: #Step2 or #Step1_Charges joined on EncounterID + Sequence"
      ],
      "self_check_hybrid_reclassification": "After applying evidence-table rules strictly: Cardiac_Cath (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; PTCA (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; Lithotripsy (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; Chemotherapy (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; IOP (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; Partial_Hospitalization (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; Observation (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; Psych (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; ECT (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID; Home_Health (agg_date=MAX, agg_enc=SUM)=HYBRID. These are moved to hybrid_categories below."
